period week early after plan b answer please alrightyy so i took plan b on july th hours after the condom broke unfortunately about days after that i had extremely extremely light bleeding for about days it was spotting i figured normal after taking the pill i wasn't due for my period till the th and i got it last night a week early i'm happy believe me lol but i thought it would make me have a late period anyone else have this i have taken it twice plan b is similar to the side effects of regular birth control pills some women have menstrual changes such as spotting or bleeding before their next period some women may have a heavier or lighter next period or a period that is early or late if your period is more than a week late you should get a pregnancy test usually if your period is early it's a sign that the pill worked mine was early both times Fertility awareness Oral contraceptive Pregnancy Emergency contraception Endometriosis Birth control Childbirth Condom Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Depo Provera Miscarriage Polycystic ovary syndrome EastEnders Obstetrics Psoriasis Intrauterine device Chemical abortion Gonorrhoea Tocopherol Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Progesterone Diabetic retinopathy Migraine Abortion Menstrual cup Breastfeeding Sexual abstinence Endometrial cancer Ovarian cyst Alanis Morissette Apollo 8 Paranoia Agent Hypertension Premature birth Acne Abortion debate Knots Landing Stroke Caffeine Sex education Puberty Eminem Vaginal bleeding Safe sex Extreme Programming Twin Billboard Hot 100 Tank classification The Emancipation of Mimi Von Willebrand disease Second Battle of El Alamein Cephalic disorder Niddah Ovarian cancer Resident Evil Outbreak Rape Estrus cycle Battle of the Somme (1916) Herpes simplex virus Sanitary towel Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Limp Bizkit Comet Shoemaker-Levy 9 USS Chicago (CA-136) Tampon Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Pelvic inflammatory disease Continuation War She Loves You Gregorian calendar Wheel of Fort